  "titles": "Lernaean Terminator Squad",
  "lore": "The Lernaeans are, like the beast that is their namesake and the icon of the Legion, an unformed legend and the object of shrouded dread. They are the grinding jaws of the many-headed Hydra, the furious assault from the unexpected quarter. And like the beast of myth, they are all but impossible to slay. The Lernaeans are clad in Cataphractii plate chased with baroque finer)’ and are armed with volkite chargers, making them fearsome close assault and spearhead units against which few enemies can stand. Having secured their objective, they hold it stubbornly like the great beast with its jaws clamped firmly about its doomed prey.",
